item.title: Fruity Dream Booth
item.description: The Fruity Dream Booth initial concept was to send pictures taken by a Raspberry Pi based photo-booth through the Google DeepDream library and tweet out the results. The challenges and computing requirements for Google Deep Dream made doing this unfeasible on a Raspberry Pi. hacking project learning through pain success The project team for Fruity Dream Booth: ferrio - core web server teknofire - javascript tweaking and moral support vlraymond - twitter data feed setup, coding and passion dayne - general idea, infrastructure, and glue The project code is hosted at dayne/fruitydreambooth
